					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I aaaaaalmost included an Able fangirl letter, but ultimately decided against it, both for in-universe and out-of-universe reasons.</p> <p>In-universe, I think it would be far more likely that the Lizerd get caught on camera than Able, just by sheer virtue of their social styles and containment procedures. Able is deep, deeeeeep underground, and Lizerd is fairly easily viewed, if hard to kill.</p> <p>Out-of-universe, I only wanted to include one heritage skip, and the reptile has my heart.</p> 
				 	]]>
