				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1310217#post-2351923</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1310217/six-letters-addressed-to-the-scp-foundation-and-one-letter-h#post-2351923</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 04 Aug 2015 21:33:01 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Agent MacLeod</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1922529</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm pretty sure she doesn't even use names for things. She just kinda thinks in terms of whether she's killed something or not yet. Like, she only sees things as 1) not needing to be killed, 2) killed already, 3) on the queue of things to be killed.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
