				<wikidot:authorName>ahbonjour</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2060840</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Solely aesthetics. I was trying to present this as a &quot;found letters&quot; thing, and a found letter wouldn't have a translation attached. I think I may add a translation in my first comment.</p> 
				 	]]>
